<p><abbr title="Easy Digital Downloads">EDD</abbr> Guest Registration will output the username, first name, and last names fields as well as password fields. The shortcode allows a few attributes to add or remove fields. See the codex below.</p>
<p><big>Current Version: <strong>1.1.9</strong> <em>Last updated: 3/29/13</em></big></p>

