<p>The EDD AJAX Check Username plugin requires EDD and will deactivate itself when it isn&#8217;t present.</p>
<p>EDD AJAX Check Username only loads its <code>CSS</code> and <code>jS</code> on the checkout/registration page saving extra bandwidth and loading time.</p>
<p>The AJAX checks against illegal usernames, illegal characters and letters and returns an error when present. Current default illegal usernames are: <code>www, web, root, admin, main, invite, administrator</code>. You can add additional names by filtering in your own, see codex below. </p>
<p>There is a default minimum character length of three (3) characters, but if you would like more or less see the example function below.</p>
